Paper: hep-th/0005162

Date: 2000-05-17

Title: Exponential Hierarchy From Spacetime Variable String Vacua

Authors: P. Berglund, T. Hubsch and D. Minic

Comments: 22 pages, Latex, 2 figures

Journal-ref: JHEP 0009 (2000) 015

It is shown that non-supersymmetric spacetime varying string vacua can leadto an exponential hierarchy between the electroweak and the gravitationalscales. The hierarchy is naturally generated by a string coupling of O(1).